{"tid":2185853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土研究社：請政府交代粉嶺哥爾夫球場是否已獲秘密續約","createTime":"2020-09-02T14:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T14:04:57.000Z","uid":285523,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fd04bdce815f750223b577f206f775c7cfe3c11f","tid":2185853,"uid":285523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"面積達 172 公頃嘅粉嶺哥爾夫球場，地契已於前日（2020 年 8 月 31 日）到期。現時一啲續約嘅消息都無。<br />\n<br />\n本研社噚日（9 月 1 日）查冊，都係無發現。公眾對於地價同條款一無所知，甚至連「等待註冊的契約」一欄，都係空嘅，係咪代表政府已經為球場秘密續約？請政府澄清：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【地價】</span>是否已以賤價繼續批出面積達 172 公頃嘅寶貴土地俾富豪打波？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【年期】</span>新地契簽幾多年？如果同上一份地契年期一樣為 21 年，2026/27 年後，是否不用跟隨「交市值三分一地價」嘅政策？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【房屋發展】</span>當中 32 公頃作房屋發展嘅土地設三年「過渡期」，詳情是甚麼？會否三年又三年？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【開放政策】</span>有否訂立新條款，要求球場唔好再「扮開放」比市民用？係咪繼續只開放 weekdays、日出同日落時間，呢啲唔啱打 golf，亦唔會有打工仔得閒嘅時段比公眾？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【開放資料】</span>有否訂立新條款，令政府可以開放球場交俾民政局，交代使用量嘅季度報告（quarterly reports）？以往政府借條款之便，利用「第三方資料」理由唔肯公開季度報告，令公眾無法得悉球場點樣使用土地<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為社會焦點轉移，就可以「側側膊，唔多覺」延續土地特權，請公眾一同 send email 打電話問清楚球場契約嘅最新狀態！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/118698568_Ax7Nx_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F118698568_Ax7Nx_1200x0.jpg&h=5f5853e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/118478389_yDC7G_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F118478389_yDC7G_1200x0.png&h=1708996c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持本土研究社研究工作  <a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=62e098ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us/</a><br />\n本土研究社 Facebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/3361138087315574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fposts%2F3361138087315574&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=d02c96b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/3361138087315574</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/請政府交代粉嶺哥爾夫球場是否已獲秘密續約/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%89%E5%B6%BA%E5%93%A5%E7%88%BE%E5%A4%AB%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B7%B2%E7%8D%B2%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E7%BA%8C%E7%B4%84%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=89155300\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%89%E5%B6%BA%E5%93%A5%E7%88%BE%E5%A4%AB%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B7%B2%E7%8D%B2%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E7%BA%8C%E7%B4%84%2F&h=af95c9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/請政府交代粉嶺哥爾夫球場是否已獲秘密續約/</a>"}]}